description.narrative: By 2022, the government has strengthened capacities to develop, manage and use M&E systems addressing the situation of children in Myanmar,which contributes to Child Poverty / Public Finance For Children, Cross-Sectoral Monitoring, Data And Situation Analyses, Evaluation And Research, Evaluation And Research (Covid), Operations Support To Programme Delivery. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Evaluations, Research And Data, Operational Support To Programme Delivery, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: Improved policy environment, budgets and systems for all children, especially the most excluded, guided by improved knowledge and disaggregated data
